{"title":"新打夯歌","authors":["刘划"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":10,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新打夯歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瓦工余师傅编了一个新打夯歌，一群夯工一边打一边唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬起石夯用力打，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗨哟嘿哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右派好比烂泥巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗨哟嘿哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们工人力量大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗨哟嘿哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右派如不来投降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗨哟嘿哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们打得他粉骨碎渣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咳嗨咦哟嗬嘿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志们问他为啥要编歌，他说：“不唱歌来不开心，唱给右派来听听！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（西北第一工程公司  刘划）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}